{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=235307535ead159f718c186152c7f866&src=http%3A%2F%2Fc.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F0eb30f2442a7d9338a304e5fa54bd11373f00105.jpg","summary":"湖南工艺美术职业学院(Hunan Arts and Crafts Vocational College)位于湖南省益阳市，是全国4所工艺美术职业学院之一、全国100所国家示范性(骨干)高职院校建设单位之一、国家首批现代学徒制试点单位、湖南省非物质文化遗产保护研究基地。学院前身是创建于1975年的益阳市七·二一工艺美术大学和成立于1981年的湖南省服装技工学校。2005年，经湖南省人民政府批准，正式成立湖南工艺美术职业学院。截至2015年12月，学校校区占地384亩，建筑面积近17.5万平方米，教学仪器设备总值5007.67万元，图书馆藏书39.75万册；设有2个二级学院、4系2部等教学单位，开设18个专科专业；有教职工388人，全日制在校生6500人。","tags":["艺术类","专科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"1975","所在地区":"益阳市秀峰公园西大门","院校隶属":"湖南省"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=60fa76c469c7a793527e0c3ac82faced&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3671651654%2C719542936%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=f8cbf3f4ba00976089aacecafd27177c&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3681283184%2C782834987%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=01e53658e802a411e4603cf71960325d&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3672142470%2C589842779%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=3415e75b5ca67c18f7a0d19e638969f9&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3668075238%2C809542343%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=4b72007ce27ed53a7bf04c8fc70206e6&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3589236741%2C748716884%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/tim